{"tid":2071843,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"拒區議會查TG 民政處或遭覆核","createTime":"2020-06-20T06:57:34.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-20T06:57:34.000Z","uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"5996af98a79bd74a3a3a61627a354382dee7be40","tid":2071843,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-20T06:57:34.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200620/RAZOFRBK6YXXACCI6QHUIWPCTA/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200620%2FRAZOFRBK6YXXACCI6QHUIWPCTA%2F&d=WBYYCruE%2BO8aOQq6cZO2w9UsrLV3ynd9sCeqRx8pZcg%3D&h=a4c970b3\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200620%2FRAZOFRBK6YXXACCI6QHUIWPCTA%2F&h=a50a414c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200620/RAZOFRBK6YXXACCI6QHUIWPCTA/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n拒區議會查TG 民政處或遭覆核<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/NT46AAEL5JBH4OU6ZSZ7TCKACM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FNT46AAEL5JBH4OU6ZSZ7TCKACM.jpg&h=79d8b190&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n袁海文（中）稱深水區會計劃眾籌，擬提出司法覆核或調查區內催淚彈粒子水平。夏家朗攝<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】返送中運動以來，警方於多區催淚彈放題，。。。。。，懷疑有政府干預，計劃向民政處提出司法覆核。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n深水埗議員疑政府干預<br />\n<br />\n深水埗區議會健康及安全社區工作小組4月29日通過調查催淚彈對該區居民、社區和環境影響，。。。。。，稱調查不屬地區事宜，不符合區議會條例，拒絕發信。<br />\n<br />\n袁海文指區會已按民政處要求將條文改成「區內的催淚彈」，但民政處仍指調查是全港性，不符合區會職能。<br />\n<br />\n袁稱民政處回覆指「政府認為不符合」，懷疑背後有保安局或警務處干預。深水埗區會計劃眾籌，目標金額至少10萬，將用於提出司法覆核或調查區內催淚彈粒子水平。區議會副主席伍月蘭認為民政處決定有政治目的，「一掂到警察引伸出嚟嘅問題就漠視唔做」。<br />\n<br />\n■記者譚名傑"}]}